it.unitn.lifecoach.model

Class ProductScore

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.unitn.lifecoach.model.ProductScore

  • public class ProductScore
extends Object
    Represents a product score object. This object contains information such as list of nutrient and their values. Also it contains product score, which is relative measure of how healthy is the food. The product score is retrieved from http://api.foodessentials.com/

    The following schema fragment specifies the expected content contained within this class. 

     <complexType name="productScore">
   <complexContent>
     <restriction base="{http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema}anyType">
       <sequence>
         <element name="nutrients" type="{http://ws.food.adapter.isde/}nutrient" maxOccurs="unbounded" minOccurs="0"/>
         <element name="productScore" type="{http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema}long"/>
         <element name="upc" type="{http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema}string" minOccurs="0"/>
       </sequence>
     </restriction>
   </complexContent>
 </complexType>
